snippet.title: Green Project - Trailer
snippet.description:
An open world survival/farmer game on mobile and PC. 
Available on Google Play Store and coming soon on PC.
If you want to follow us: " https://twitter.com/GreenProject13 "

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ZeroneGames.GreenProject
